# 🐍 Python for Cybersecurity Roadmap

Welcome to my Python for Cybersecurity learning repository.

This repository contains my complete journey from Python basics to advanced cybersecurity automation. Every phase includes small practice programs to understand concepts and one practical project that combines everything learned in that phase.

---

## 🎯 Objective

- Learn Python from scratch
- Build strong programming fundamentals
- Automate repetitive tasks
- Develop cybersecurity tools
- Prepare for Bug Bounty and Penetration Testing
- Build a professional GitHub portfolio

